newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,653 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,653 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 1,653 contracts compared to 727 overnight Thursday.
There were 253 wheat, 483 corn, 778 soybean, 98 soymeal, 38 soyoil, two wheat put and one soybean call traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1/4 cent higher to one cent lower, corn was steady to two cents lower and soybeans were five to eight cents per bushel lower.
